					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Everyone who has played on both emulator and on real NES probably has noticed how different they look visually. NES has some blurry edges, slightly inconsistent color (some colors changing slightly), contrast issues (might be the TV as well, but not sure), a bit of motion blur, scanlines not perfectly aligned and so on. Does any emulator have a filter that would at least try to make it look like what it would look like on NES?</div>

