						<div class="postbody">I use nintedulator if i want to get close to something like an NTSC experience (or what i imagine it to be). For PAL, i just use my old unit because nothing i've tried emulator-wise looks quite like it. One thing you don't get in emulation so far is how different the APU + audio out actually sounds.<br /><br />btw is there really motion blur? that's not something i've noticed.</div>

					
