					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Nestopia has had an NTSC filter for ages, based on accurately modelling the NTSC signal generation and decoding process.<br /><br />So called &quot;CRT filters&quot; on the other hand are usually just toys, rarely-ever accurate to the characteristics of any real-life CRT, and so best avoided.</div>

